{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"308b4e5c91","title":"在十五省、市委书记会议上的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ea008bda29","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":17,"articleId":"308b4e5c91"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5430eba543","type":"title","text":"在十五省、市委书记会议上的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"fa32f77f47","type":"paragraph","text":"（广西省汇报时）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"f09d7dbc69","type":"paragraph","text":"一万七千个社缩一二百，小事。发展五千个社，少吧！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"9964149f15","type":"paragraph","text":"（湖南省汇报时）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"6cd81e203b","type":"paragraph","text":"怪不得湖南不叫。（指粮食工作）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"08e1e54895","type":"paragraph","text":"发展四千个，这么少，不到一番呀！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"f19175bfd2","type":"paragraph","text":"（江西省汇报时）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"e1315c4715","type":"paragraph","text":"发展八千个，百分之三十四的乡。再发展一万四千个。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"9cc60bd295","type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北省汇报时）","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"a3c3ac24dd","type":"paragraph","text":"周转粮不能没有，不放入计划，好呀！不买过头粮，不计周","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"f3259394a1","type":"subtitle","text":"转粮。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"37574fdc07","type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江省汇报时","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"1b6aae28c8","type":"paragraph","text":"现在五万五千个，已退七千个，再退三千个，尚余四万五千空白乡还要发展，其余各省可否翻一番","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"9fcb7abe39","type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏省汇报时）","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"17829043b3","type":"paragraph","text":"落后乡百分之五有反革命，百分之十环人、蜕化分子，这是反革命同盟军，县区乡三级干部要调查。不能让中农做主，中农可以教育，他要按党的政策办事也可以","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"e94cd26dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"三万二千个不发展？！要比一比浙江","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"89e1799b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"（安徽省汇报时）","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"97a8e1600d","type":"paragraph","text":"不发达的省，要利用发达省的经验。江苏赶上去，湘鄂两广要放手发展。合作社多数要大发展，百分之九十较好，百分之十退。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"f061886f68","type":"paragraph","text":"（山东省汇报时）","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"58ad27400a","type":"paragraph","text":"死人真省粮？湖南说死几十人，只死一人。现象、本质分开，一股台风天黑了，不得了。一查，是假的，合作社百分之九十是好的，是经多次风的。再讲几点：","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"40352173a5","type":"paragraph","text":"一、证明百分之三至百分之五，机动幅度再研究，不决定。八百八十亿，十一亿重点减。湖南、安徽、山东要加一点。交粮食会议，为粮食需要者设。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"5877493297","type":"paragraph","text":"二、层层负责有好处，但会形成无数独立王国。二十多万个要统一、分级。统一计划下各省负责。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"014055cd36","type":"paragraph","text":"三、周转粮、细粮、粗粮照旧。不要在粮食上舞整，供应太广。口口缺是假缺。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"b67a250ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"四、合作社自愿互利，如果自愿，要拍板。承认了的，照着办，保证百分之九十可靠。","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"3da1dedc14","type":"paragraph","text":"五、习、法、公核有争执，党委统一，合法又敏觉，做好。绕、潘、杨案子，包底三个反革命。用大叛徒胡京和。可以传达到十四级以上。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"},{"id":"8871c18424","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风案子另发通知，那个字号不清楚","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91"}],"page":{"id":"ac5529ad9c","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"308b4e5c91","start":87,"end":88}}}},"__N_SSG":true}